Concert of the "Students of the Same Revolution" with singing ensembles of the Karlsuniversity
For the third time, the Festival Festa Academica offers the reconciling of the World Student Day with the anniversary of the Samten Revolution and this together with music experience.
In the course of the festival, the twenty professional and university choirs will present themselves.
The festival will focus on the two concerts that will take place on November 17.
"The Karlsuniversität has a large share in the festival."
"The choir of the Faculty of Education and the Faculty of Humanistic Studies is also represented among the participants and the festival committee is also the rector Václav Hampl," said Jakub Čaloun, head of the organization team.
