It is also very unusual that a band like yours has remained with the same musicians for so long.
Yes, four of us have been playing together for 21 years and Matt (Cameron) met us 13 years ago. This alone is much more time than many bands last.
First of all, I believe that we all appreciate being alive and we also take care of each other.
We are all close friends, which is why musical paths have opened up, giving each individual freedom to experiment.
One trusts the other and his music. We could not be any better.
Your relationship to fame has not always been easy. On the other hand, thanks to your success, you have always been able to do what you wanted.
How do you find a balance?
