Modol, like Roldán and Bayona with urban experience, considers the proposal to be a "intellectual challenge" that poses "some dangers".
Dangers resulting from the "insecurity that the design of a public space nowadays brings with it" following the experience of the 1980s, which had their "swan song" in the area of the forum.
