Bayona suggests that the answer to the question in the heading of this article is complex, as in the terms of the tender a global view of Collserola was missing: "There were 16 competitions in the cross-section," he says, "on the axis mountain lake. But there is no longitudinal perspective that the area as a whole looks at."
At least in his case, this led him to participate in the 16 competitions.
